  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> </font><b>This\n        music crept ...</b><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p>V. <i>The Tempest</i>, as above. [Eliot's note]<b> </b>Cf.\n        line 48. The line is from Ferdinand's speech, continuing\n        after \"weeping again the King my father's\n        wrack.\"</p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>Shakespeare,<i> The Tempest</i></td>\n<td><a href=\"title_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Waste_A.htm\"><font>back to \"The Waste Land\" </font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
